page.title: 10SECONDARY SCHOOL DETAILS
page.content: SECONDARY SCHOOL PROJECT 1.How many classes are there?15. 2.When was it built?In 1958. 3.When do you start school here?11 or 12. 4.Who is the head teacher?Mr.Beams. 5.What age do you leave?16. 6.When do you start your tests?At 16. 7.How many years are you in school?5. 8.For break,do you go on field?Yes. 9.Do you do games on the field?Yes. 10.How many children are there in school?350. 11.What lessons do you do? English Language. English Literature. French Language. French Studies. Maths.Art Geography.P.E. Craft.Woodwork. Metalwork.Technology.
